## Deployment Checklist & Sources

- **Accessibility:** Ensure `<meta charset>` and `<meta viewport>` remain for mobile; use semantic HTML (e.g. `<main>`, proper `<label>` associations)【1†L19-L27】【3†L31-L39】.  
- **Security Headers:** Deploy with HTTPS/HSTS. No inline scripts or styles (we have inline for demo; in real app use CSP). Add `<meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'self';">` on server side to prevent XSS【turn3search3†L0-L3】.  
- **Input Validation:** Though filters are static selects, ensure any user-entered data (if extended) is sanitized. We use `encodeURIComponent` for query params (e.g. in `property.html?id=…`) to avoid injection.  
- **Performance:** For many listings, consider pagination or lazy loading. (Not needed for MVP static list.)  
- **Privacy:** No sensitive data handled here beyond user’s own listing interest link; no PII collected on this page.  
- **Logging & Monitoring:** Log filter errors or script exceptions.  

